Comparison
	Over time
		Few period
			Many categories          :Line chart
			Single or few categories :Bar chart
		Many periods
			Non cyclical data        :Line chart
			Cyclical data            :Circular area chart
	Among item                   :Bar chart
Distribution
	Single variable              :Histogram chart
	Tow variable                 :Scatter chart
	Three variable               :3D area chart

Composition
	Static
		Component of component     :Stacked 100% column chart
		Accumulation to total      :Waterfall chart
		hare of total              :Pie chart
	Over time
		Many periods               :Stacked area chart
		Few periods                :Stacked column chart

Relationship
	Tow variable                 :Scater chart
	Thress variable              :Babble chart




